  "remarks": "QDi.074\nPassport no.: Tunisian passport number E590976, issued on 19 Jun. 1987 expired on 18 Jun 1992. Belgian nationality withdrawn on 26 Jan. 2009.\nIn detention in Nivelles, Belgium, as of Oct. 2010. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 8 Jun. 2010. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 4 Dec. 2019. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2610 (2021) was concluded on 30 October 2023.; Listing: Listed by UN 1267 Committee on 3 Sep. 2002 (amended on 26 November 2004 and 20 December 2005, 31 July 2006 and 3 Jul 2007, 10 Aug 2009, 25 Jan. 2010 and 23 Dec. 2010, 6 Dec 2019, 30 Oct. 2023).",
